KxJRT
Interface IKxJModelInput

All Known Subinterfaces:
IKxJModelInputWithNames
All Known Implementing Classes:
KxFileReader, KxFileReaderWithNames, KxInputReader, KxJModelInputMapper
public interface IKxJModelInput

The Automatic Analytics Java model input interface. A class implementing this interface is able to provide the model with input data values it needs.

See Also:
apply
